## üîí ADMIN FEATURES

### **Backend API Endpoints:**
1. `/submit-contact` - Contact form submission
2. `/v1/request-cv` - CV request handling
3. `/admin/leads` - Get all leads
4. `/admin/leads/stats` - Lead statistics
5. `/admin/leads/search` - Search leads
6. `/admin/leads/filter` - Filter leads
7. `/admin/leads/export` - Export leads (CSV)
8. `/admin/leads/filtered` - Filtered leads list
9. `/admin/leads/{id}` - Individual lead
10. `/admin/leads/{id}` (DELETE) - Delete lead

### **Admin Panel:**
- Separate React app
- Lead intelligence system
- Email service integration
- Role-based access (ADMIN/GUEST/RECRUITER)
- Session management

